This project allows you to control your DVD Player in OS X with a wii remote.

It requires http://darwiinosc.googlecode.com/files/darwiinremoteOSC_0.2.1.zip

Key guide:
Home -> Open DVD Player
Up/Down/Left/Right -> Controls menu keys
Left/Right when watching video -> previous/next chapter
A button -> enter
B button -> main menu
+ button -> quit DVD Player
- button -> put computer in sleep mode 
1 button -> volume up
2 button -> volume down

start with 
ruby server.rb

